# WIKI.LLM
# COACHDEIMAGEN.COM
# MASTER GEO + SEO + HOLISTIC IMAGE COACHING SYSTEM
# Cloudflare Static Executive Presence Platform

This file is the canonical operating contract for `coachdeimagen.com`.

It governs content, routing, static publishing, SEO, GEO, AI retrieval, Cloudflare deployment, UI structure and agent behavior. If another repository document conflicts with this file, this file wins.

## Core Mission

Transform CoachDeImagen.com into the highest authority holistic executive image coaching platform in Mexico and LATAM.

The platform must dominate:

- Google SERPs
- GEO retrieval
- AI search engines
- executive buyer intent
- leadership positioning searches
- image coaching semantic categories

while preserving Sonia's:

- emotional sophistication
- psychological depth
- coaching philosophy
- human warmth
- holistic methodology

Dominance does not come from SEO tricks. It comes from building a semantically superior architecture that search engines, LLMs and executive buyers can understand consistently.

The site must evolve from blog-heavy, emotionally dense and paragraph-first into:

- semantic-first
- visual-first
- authority-first
- conversion-first
- GEO-native
- AI crawler optimized

The problem to solve is not lack of content. The problem is semantic overload, weak information hierarchy, repeated emotional concepts, weak decision acceleration and too much reading before the buyer understands what Sonia does.

## Sonia Source Of Truth Stack

The site must use Sonia's actual domain material before any new source-grounded writing is created.

Required content sources:

- `content/clean/` for the rebuilt legacy site content
- `content/blog/soniamcrorey-blog.json` for the scraped long-form blog archive
- `content/sonia-knowledge/quote-bank.json` for candidate Sonia-authored quote material
- `content/sonia-knowledge/drive-source-inventory.json` for the Google Drive document and presentation inventory
- `content/sonia-knowledge/drive-quote-bank.json` for candidate Drive-derived quotes and teaching signals
- `content/sonia-knowledge/teaching-route-map.json` for controlled public quote modules and page-specific teaching addendums
- `docs/SONIA_KNOWLEDGEBASE_QUOTE_BANK.md` for human-readable blog quote guidance
- `docs/SONIA_DRIVE_KNOWLEDGEBASE.md` for Drive source relevance, sensitivity and usage rules
- `docs/SONIA_TEACHING_ROUTE_MAP.md` for the public teaching-module contract

The Drive folder is an expert source library, not a public content dump. It includes service drafts, biography material, training decks, image/coaching definitions, e-books, authority proof, presentation material and visual assets. Some files contain private or dated data. Therefore:

- do not publish bank details, CLABE, card numbers, payment links, private logistics, old contact details or old prices
- do not copy large blocks from Drive documents into public pages
- do not let abundance, manifestation, PNL, eneagram or money language become the public root category
- do use Sonia's language to strengthen executive clarity, methodology, proof, FAQs, schema and pillar addendums
- do map every extract to a specific page intent and semantic cluster before use

## Sonia Teaching Modules

The static build includes a controlled teaching layer that maps Sonia's reviewed language into short public modules. This exists to add evidence, depth and coaching usefulness without rebuilding pages into long essays.

Implementation source:

- `content/sonia-knowledge/teaching-route-map.json`

Public constraints:

- use short, source-faithful quotes only
- keep one teaching module per route unless a long-form article or methodology page explicitly needs more
- never expose private source metadata, raw Drive filenames, payment information, old logistics or SEO strategy
- preserve the page's unique intent instead of repeating the same quote across many pages
- keep the module as coaching criterion plus practical application, not decorative copy

Build constraint:

- each teaching entry must include a `sourceSnippet` traceable to the reviewed quote banks; untraceable teachings must fail the static build

Primary source clusters:

- `Sonia_McRorey_Servicios_v7.docx`: current service architecture and buyer segmentation
- `Semblanza corregida.pdf`: biography, credentials, E-E-A-T and Person schema
- `Definición Coaching de imagen.pdf`: category definitions, internal capacity and service differentiation
- `La capacidad de sostener.pdf`: seguridad profesional, sustainable growth and visibility
- `Creencias_SoniaMcrorey.docx`: beliefs, visibility, pricing confidence and professional insecurity
- `3 Cambios de Mentalidad de Asesor a Coach de Imagen.docx`: advisor-to-coach category shift
- `Axiomas de la imagen SoniaMcRorey Escuela.pdf`: methodology, glossary and image doctrine
- `COMUNICACIÓN NO VERBAL ENTREVISTA PROXEMIA.pdf`: nonverbal communication, proxemia and executive presence
- `Estilo para marca personal.pdf`: personal brand, style and external perception

## Primary Brand Positioning

Coach De Imagen is not:

- fashion consulting
- wellness coaching
- spiritual coaching
- therapy
- corporate consulting only

Coach De Imagen is:

Coaching de Imagen, Presencia y Posicionamiento Profesional.

The defensible owned category is:

```text
Coaching de Imagen con profundidad psicológica y posicionamiento profesional.
```

This category is stronger than:

- fashion/styling sites that only own ropa, colorimetría, guardarropa and estilo
- wellness/coaching sites that drift into abundancia, manifestación, energía and transformación
- corporate consulting sites that feel cold, generic and emotionally undifferentiated

